                          ------------
       Marathonmod X11 Font: A minor mod of one of my favorite font from the nucleus family
                     https://github.com/DaisukeAramaki/Dotfiles
                
INSTALLATION:
1. Move the font to /usr/local/lib/X11/fonts/ (Note: This is the path for BSD, on Linux it should be different, so check that out first)
2. Run mkfontdir, fc-cache -f -v 
3. Update fontpath in xorg.conf or .xinitrc, depending on whether you use a conf file for X or not.

